00:49:38,858 --> 00:49:40,532
Did you confirm it
with Cho Dae-gook's side?

751
00:49:41,813 --> 00:49:45,453
Yes. I couldn't believe it either,
so I checked with the Team Leader.

752
00:49:46,175 --> 00:49:48,272
According to the conversation he had
with the prison officer,

753
00:49:48,667 --> 00:49:52,864
Seo Bum-Jo and Cho Dae-gook
did have contact.

754
00:49:54,697 --> 00:49:56,707
The timing is artistic.

755
00:49:57,123 --> 00:49:59,457
He's blowing this up on the day of
his mother's grand opening ceremony?

756
00:50:01,250 --> 00:50:02,217
Sir.

757
00:50:02,617 --> 00:50:04,348
Do we have to see this as
he's turning himself in?

758
00:50:09,370 --> 00:50:10,851
Yeonjoo BJ Square
Grand Opening Ceremony

759
00:50:21,100 --> 00:50:23,836
I'm on my way to the ceremony.

760
00:50:25,247 --> 00:50:26,364
What are you talking about?

761
00:50:27,000 --> 00:50:29,284
Chairwoman's son ordered a murder?

762
00:50:32,351 --> 00:50:34,788
There are so many eyes as they are...

763
00:50:36,437 --> 00:50:38,629
I understand. Hang up.

764
00:50:41,397 --> 00:50:44,564
I'm not going to the ceremony anymore.
Turn the car around.

765
00:50:45,717 --> 00:50:48,411
Sir. It's the Chief from
Han River Police Station.

766
00:50:48,511 --> 00:50:51,781
He says Chairwoman's son just
turned himself in for ordering a murder.

767
00:50:52,071 --> 00:50:52,879
What?

768
00:51:21,891 --> 00:51:25,641
- You didn't set it up last time.
- What is this?

769
00:51:26,809 --> 00:51:28,738
They said all the assemblymen
were going to come.

770
00:51:29,161 --> 00:51:30,427
Why is it so empty?

771
00:51:32,927 --> 00:51:35,221
I know.
They've should've been here a while ago.

772
00:51:49,861 --> 00:51:50,921
What's wrong?

773
00:51:51,021 --> 00:51:53,111
Why aren't the assemblymen coming?
Call them now.

774
00:51:53,385 --> 00:51:54,917
Ma'am.

775
00:52:07,591 --> 00:52:10,162
Ma'am. Are you alright?

776
00:52:12,861 --> 00:52:13,653
Help me.

777
00:52:14,817 --> 00:52:16,675
Over here. Quickly!

778
00:52:21,927 --> 00:52:23,061
Ma'am. Are you alright?

779
00:52:23,901 --> 00:52:25,038
What's wrong with her?

780
00:52:26,021 --> 00:52:27,548
Is something wrong?

781
00:52:35,134 --> 00:52:35,980
Yes Captain.

782
00:52:37,222 --> 00:52:39,778
Excuse me? Seo Bum-Jo turned himself in?

783
00:52:41,151 --> 00:52:43,247
What are you talking about?
He turned himself in?

784
00:52:44,571 --> 00:52:47,181
- Yes. Captain.
- What? He turned himself in?

785
00:52:47,281 --> 00:52:49,291
- Ordering a murder?
- That attack?

786
00:52:49,391 --> 00:52:51,388
- Chairwoman Park's son ordered that?
- Interview her?

787
00:52:51,498 --> 00:52:54,308
- Seo Bum-Jo did?
- Yes. I understand, Captain.

788
00:52:55,178 --> 00:52:58,598
- Seo Bum-Jo, you bastard.
- What? What's going on?

789
00:52:59,222 --> 00:53:00,698
He confessed that he ordered Cho Dae-gook

790
00:53:00,798 --> 00:53:02,328
to attack us and turned himself in.

791
00:53:03,057 --> 00:53:03,805
What?

792
00:53:04,538 --> 00:53:05,805
He's not answering his phone.

793
00:53:06,599 --> 00:53:08,888
It looks like he went in
instead of his mother.

794
00:53:09,310 --> 00:53:10,508
Why did he...?

795
00:53:12,758 --> 00:53:14,278
This is great. I can just ask you.

796
00:53:14,378 --> 00:53:18,410
If you end up interviewing my mother
at the ceremony...

797
00:53:21,049 --> 00:53:22,492
can you tell her something for me?

798
00:53:23,998 --> 00:53:26,325
- No way...
- What's wrong?

799
00:53:27,848 --> 00:53:32,312
I saw Bum-Jo earlier.
He asked a strange favor.

800
00:53:33,366 --> 00:53:34,658
A favor? What favor?

801
00:53:36,327 --> 00:53:37,685
Do you admit everything?

802
00:53:44,229 --> 00:53:48,668
He asked me tell Chairwoman Park
something if I end up interviewing her.

803
00:53:57,138 --> 00:53:59,752
Do you know that your son
just turned himself in?

804
00:53:59,852 --> 00:54:01,934
Did he do it alone?

805
00:54:02,034 --> 00:54:03,745
Do you know why he ordered the attack?

806
00:54:03,845 --> 00:54:06,382
Why do you think he ordered an attack?

807
00:54:06,482 --> 00:54:08,940
Did you sense that he would do
something like that recently?

808
00:54:09,040 --> 00:54:12,078
- Move aside. Move aside.
- No interviews.

809
00:54:12,830 --> 00:54:17,024
Chairwoman Park. You son asked me to
tell you something just earlier.

810
00:54:17,124 --> 00:54:18,456
Would it be okay for me to tell you?

811
00:54:22,804 --> 00:54:23,961
Seo Bum-Jo?

812
00:54:24,061 --> 00:54:25,994
Hey, did you interview Seo Bum-Jo?

813
00:54:28,286 --> 00:54:31,738
If you end up interviewing my mother
at the ceremony...

814
00:54:32,846 --> 00:54:34,242
can you tell her something for me?

815
00:54:34,814 --> 00:54:35,880
What do you want me to tell her?

816
00:54:36,121 --> 00:54:37,714
Everything I've enjoyed...

817
00:54:38,633 --> 00:54:40,448
and everything I'll enjoy in the future...

818
00:54:42,151 --> 00:54:44,218
I'll take responsibility
with mother for that.

819
00:54:44,321 --> 00:54:45,663
Your son wanted me to tell you that...

820
00:54:46,708 --> 00:54:48,202
"everything I've enjoyed..."

821
00:54:48,625 --> 00:54:50,421
"and everything I'll enjoy
in the future..."

822
00:54:51,086 --> 00:54:53,451
"I'll take responsibility
with mother for that."

823
00:54:56,852 --> 00:54:59,662
- What is he talking about?
- Does that mean that she participated?

824
00:55:02,579 --> 00:55:06,143
Tell her that I'm sorry for leaving her
alone and pretending not to know.

825
00:55:06,955 --> 00:55:08,471
He told me to tell you that he's sorry

826
00:55:08,571 --> 00:55:10,282
"for leaving you alone and
pretending not to know."

827
00:55:14,392 --> 00:55:15,470
Tell my her that, from now on...

828
00:55:18,154 --> 00:55:19,739
I'll always be with her.

829
00:55:21,574 --> 00:55:22,422
Please tell her that.

830
00:55:23,789 --> 00:55:28,727
He wanted me to tell you that
he'll be with you always from now on.

831
00:55:34,691 --> 00:55:37,951
- So they're accomplices.
- That means Chairwoman Park participated.

832
00:55:38,051 --> 00:55:40,061
Is she telling the truth?

833
00:55:40,161 --> 00:55:42,772
She's a Pinocchio so she can't lie.
It's the truth.

834
00:55:45,664 --> 00:55:47,295
Where is my son right now?

835
00:55:49,585 --> 00:55:51,341
He's at Han River Police Station.

836
00:55:54,642 --> 00:55:57,371
Move aside. Move aside.

837
00:56:12,899 --> 00:56:15,234
I think Bum-Jo really wanted
to tell her this.

838
00:56:18,001 --> 00:56:22,897
This interview probably can't go out
from MSC, right?

839
00:56:23,383 --> 00:56:25,361
Yeah. Probably.

840
00:56:25,461 --> 00:56:28,918
- Yes. It seems the son was interviewed.
- He hinted that they were accomplices.

841
00:56:29,018 --> 00:56:32,518
- If it's true, it's an ordered attack.
- The recent attack on the reporters.

842
00:56:32,618 --> 00:56:36,040
Yes. She left for Han River
Police Station. I'll head over there.

843
00:56:38,074 --> 00:56:41,248
But since everyone else filmed
your interview, it will be aired.

844
00:56:41,979 --> 00:56:42,788
Don't worry.

845
00:56:44,485 --> 00:56:45,691
Then it's good.

846
00:56:50,903 --> 00:56:52,824
Seo Bum-Jo

847
00:57:00,779 --> 00:57:02,579
Hey, you bastard. What did you just do?

848
00:57:02,679 --> 00:57:05,194
Speak softer. I can hear everything.

849
00:57:05,867 --> 00:57:08,289
- Why didn't you answer your phone?
- I was in the interrogation.

850
00:57:09,493 --> 00:57:11,112
They said I'll be going to
a holding cell soon.

851
00:57:11,975 --> 00:57:13,594
This will be the last phone call.

852
00:57:15,077 --> 00:57:16,377
Tell them that you didn't do it.

853
00:57:16,838 --> 00:57:20,246
I know why you're doing this
but this isn't right.

854
00:57:21,861 --> 00:57:23,386
If you know, just stay out of it.

855
00:57:25,613 --> 00:57:28,139
- This is the only way.
- Seo Bum-Jo!

856
00:57:32,945 --> 00:57:34,615
Why didn't you press me instead?

857
00:57:36,137 --> 00:57:39,544
That you resent her, hate her.

858
00:57:40,814 --> 00:57:41,957
You should've told me that.

859
00:57:43,826 --> 00:57:44,462
If you did that...

860
00:57:46,274 --> 00:57:48,330
...I could've pretended
not to know and held out longer.

861
00:57:58,443 --> 00:57:59,779
I don't have any other reason either.

862
00:58:01,671 --> 00:58:04,712
I'm doing this because
I want to reveal the truth.

863
00:58:06,976 --> 00:58:10,581
The good and the bad,
the truth of everything.

864
00:58:14,009 --> 00:58:14,937
In my own way...

865
00:58:18,079 --> 00:58:19,919
I just wanted to let the world know.

866
00:58:23,220 --> 00:58:24,369
Bum-Jo.

867
00:58:25,130 --> 00:58:28,638
Although it was brief,
I was a reporter too.

868
00:58:30,463 --> 00:58:32,061
Just why do you have to go this far?

869
00:58:33,310 --> 00:58:34,150
Just why?

870
00:58:36,429 --> 00:58:37,876
I told you before...

871
00:58:39,285 --> 00:58:40,446
that I'm on your side.

872
00:58:41,943 --> 00:58:43,648
Why would I be doing this...

873
00:58:45,325 --> 00:58:46,619
...if I wasn't on your side?

874
00:58:53,018 --> 00:58:54,166
Do you believe my words now?

875
00:58:57,074 --> 00:58:58,920
I believed you from the beginning,
you crazy bastard.
